hildon-desktop (1:2.2.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Implement Add Applet dialog. Fixes NB#88341
  * Improved switcher/launcher button managing logic. Fixes: NB#88359
  * Made the launcher prettier and more similar to the specs. Fixes: NB#88439
  * Implement storage of Applet positon. Fixes NB#89599
  * Scale the thumbnail view instead of setting its size when using fbos.
    Fixes: NB#88355
  * Corrected edit menu strings. Fixes: NB#88317
  * Added a child setup funcion called by g_spawn_async that sets up the
    correct priority and OOM unprotection. Fixes: NB#87443

